title: Whitesnake - White Night In Russia 1994 DVD - cOOt
description:
In 1990, Coverdale put Whitesnake on ice, only to reform it four years later to record a Greatest Hits album and play a supporting European tour. This DVD is of their brilliant show recorded in St. Petersburg, Russia, at the White Nights Festival in 1994.

Tracklist:

1. Intro
2. Bad Boys
3. Slide It In
4. Love Aint No Stronger
5. Judgementday
6. Is This Love
7. Guitar Solo / Adrian Vandenberg
8. Dont Leave Me This Way
9. Soldier Of Fortune
10. Smoke On The Water
11. Oi 12. Slow An Easy
13. Fool For Your Loving
14. Here I Go Again
15. Aint No Love In The Heart Of The City
16. Still Of The Night



Enjoy the show, and don't be shy about leaving comments!
